And now it's time for bed.

00:11.245 --> 00:12.745
Yes, it is.

00:12.813 --> 00:14.546
Oh.

00:14.615 --> 00:17.316
I know.
I know, I know.

00:17.418 --> 00:19.018
It's bedtime though.

00:19.120 --> 00:22.021
'Cause Mommy
knows how early
you like to wake up.

00:23.024 --> 00:24.690
Oh, yes.

00:24.792 --> 00:26.692
Hey.

00:26.794 --> 00:28.027
Goodnighty night.

