It's ok. It's ok Sadie.

01:28.456 --> 01:30.222
Ugh, not again...ugh.

01:35.062 --> 01:36.295
For heaven's sake.

01:43.471 --> 01:45.804
You're kidding me.
   Come on!

01:49.376 --> 01:51.677
Shh, shh, shh.
Shh, shh.

01:51.779 --> 01:54.213
Come on.
Come on.

01:54.315 --> 01:55.848
It's okay.

01:56.884 --> 01:59.151
Shh.

02:01.188 --> 02:02.888
Finally.

02:02.990 --> 02:04.656
Shh.

02:04.725 --> 02:09.228
<i> It's okay.</i>
    <i> Shh, shh, shh. It's okay.</i>
    <i> Daddy's here. Daddy's here.</i>

02:09.330 --> 02:11.430
Shh, shh, shh.

02:16.036 --> 02:17.536
Sadie? Sadie?

02:17.638 --> 02:20.439
Oh, my God. Sadie.

02:22.109 --> 02:23.609
Oh, my--

02:25.045 --> 02:26.879
Oh, my God.

02:26.981 --> 02:29.615
Sadie?
                        Sadie.

02:31.418 --> 02:33.719
Oh, my God.

02:36.190 --> 02:38.123
Sadie. Sadie.

02:40.127 --> 02:41.793
Sadie!

02:41.896 --> 02:44.863
Oh, my--

02:56.377 --> 02:58.777
That's
            my beautiful girl.

03:01.749 --> 03:03.782
Everything's okay.

03:03.884 --> 03:05.684
Daddy's got you now.

