♪<i> And the dish</i>
   <i> Ran away with the spoon</i> ♪

48:57.168 --> 49:01.003
I knew Matt was volatile,
 but assault?

49:01.105 --> 49:04.240
I know.
    I was really shocked too.

49:04.342 --> 49:06.876
Jealousy will do that
to a man.

49:06.978 --> 49:07.843
Jealous?

49:07.946 --> 49:09.979
Of Garrett?

49:10.081 --> 49:12.949
Matt showed up
at the restaurant to talk.

49:13.017 --> 49:15.151
He said he was suspicious
of Garrett,

49:15.219 --> 49:17.853
that he had this feeling
that there was something
wrong with him.

49:17.956 --> 49:19.822
He said
        the same thing to me.

49:19.924 --> 49:21.357
I know jealous
when I see it.

49:21.459 --> 49:23.259
Hmm.

49:23.361 --> 49:26.862
I told him he could take
a lesson or two from Garrett
on how to be a better man.

49:26.965 --> 49:29.532
You don't think that's
what set him off, do you?

49:30.568 --> 49:32.134
No.

49:32.236 --> 49:33.970
I mean,
    if I've learned anything,

49:34.072 --> 49:37.340
it's that you cannot control
    the actions of others.

49:37.442 --> 49:39.275
Like this little guy

49:39.377 --> 49:42.345
who wakes me up
        every two hours to pee.

49:43.681 --> 49:45.214
Ladies.

49:45.316 --> 49:47.883
The babies are finally asleep
and dinner is ready.

49:47.986 --> 49:50.052
Thank you.

49:50.722 --> 49:52.621
Help me up.

49:54.192 --> 49:55.291
Here you go.

49:58.096 --> 49:59.962
Ooh!

50:00.064 --> 50:01.497
I'm not sure
      I'm gonna like this.

50:01.599 --> 50:03.132
It's just an herbal mix.

50:03.201 --> 50:06.569
It's supposed
to be good for the baby.
Antioxidants and stuff.

50:06.637 --> 50:10.106
You should start
taking it every day.
It worked wonders for my wife.

50:10.208 --> 50:13.442
John,
                it smells great.
                Can I help?

50:13.544 --> 50:15.678
Nope. All done.

50:15.780 --> 50:17.646
You did not need to cook for me.

50:17.749 --> 50:20.616
Oh, it's my pleasure.

50:20.685 --> 50:24.553
Besides, it's the least I can do
after all the trouble
we've put you through.

50:24.655 --> 50:26.856
It was no trouble, really.

50:26.958 --> 50:29.125
No, but I do
            wanna say again

50:29.227 --> 50:31.427
I'm so sorry
            for what happened.

50:31.496 --> 50:33.129
Oh, no. It was my fault.

50:33.197 --> 50:36.332
You warned me,
and I should have listened.

50:36.434 --> 50:39.335
-It was worth a try, I guess.
-I bet your forehead disagrees.

50:41.039 --> 50:45.174
Well, here's to those
whom we shed from our lives

50:45.243 --> 50:48.511
and to those we let in,
   including this little guy.

50:50.348 --> 50:51.147
- Cheers.
-     Cheers.

50:52.483 --> 50:53.916
Cheers.

50:56.254 --> 50:57.853
When is the due date exactly?

50:57.922 --> 50:59.922
Well, I'm supposed
    to be induced on the 20th

51:00.024 --> 51:02.725
unless this guy wants
    to pop out a little earlier.

51:02.794 --> 51:04.894
Well, the baby bags
 are all packed.

51:04.962 --> 51:06.796
We're ready to go
whenever he decides.

51:06.898 --> 51:09.365
Maybe he'll surprise us.

51:35.960 --> 51:38.260
What's that, Daddy?

51:39.730 --> 51:42.965
That is
when your brother arrives.

51:43.034 --> 51:44.233
But why so long?

51:44.335 --> 51:46.202
Oh, it'll be here
            before you know it.

51:46.304 --> 51:48.304
And I have a lot to do
        before then.

51:48.406 --> 51:51.073
A few weeks
after he gets here,
we're taking a trip.

51:51.175 --> 51:53.075
All of us, as a family.

51:53.144 --> 51:56.812
But I need you to be
   all packed and ready to go.
      Does that sound good?

51:56.914 --> 51:58.914
Will Mommy be there?

52:21.839 --> 52:23.439
Olivia.

52:23.508 --> 52:25.074
What do you want?
I fired you.

52:25.143 --> 52:28.444
I'm aware.
        You should invite me in.

52:28.546 --> 52:30.613
Why would I wanna do that?

52:30.681 --> 52:33.315
I don't think you'd want
   to have this talk outside.

52:33.417 --> 52:35.117
Too many ears.

52:38.856 --> 52:41.457
The kids are asleep.
How have you been?

52:42.126 --> 52:43.559
Unemployed.
Hmm.

52:43.628 --> 52:46.128
Well, you did that
to yourself.

52:46.230 --> 52:48.430
So, what's this about?

52:48.533 --> 52:52.234
From the first time
            I met you,
            something felt off.

52:52.336 --> 52:55.337
The conversations
            I overheard
            when you were alone.

52:55.406 --> 52:59.275
-I told you--
        -Oh, yes. The dead wife.
               Poor thing.

52:59.343 --> 53:04.013
You know, the other night,
there was something on the telly
about a missing baby.

53:04.081 --> 53:06.949
It made me think
        about your baby, Laura,

53:07.051 --> 53:10.452
why you didn't have
        a single photo of her

53:10.555 --> 53:13.022
or of your
                other daughter.

53:13.090 --> 53:15.791
Which led me to check
        the newspapers online,

53:15.893 --> 53:17.826
and I discovered this.

53:19.197 --> 53:22.064
Maybe you'd like
        to put that in a frame.

53:23.601 --> 53:25.167
And what's this
supposed to be?

53:25.269 --> 53:29.138
That's Laura, your child,
    or so you claim.

53:29.207 --> 53:31.874
Her real name is Sadie.

53:31.976 --> 53:34.443
Oh, don't bother
            with another lie.

53:34.545 --> 53:38.447
We both have
            far better things
            to do with our time.

53:39.483 --> 53:42.885
Besides, I know
                your real name,

53:42.987 --> 53:44.620
David Miller.

53:44.722 --> 53:46.622
I almost called the police.

53:46.724 --> 53:49.391
And then
                I had a thought.

53:49.460 --> 53:52.995
Maybe we could come
            to an arrangement.

53:53.064 --> 53:54.430
You're blackmailing me.

53:54.532 --> 53:57.666
No, love.
    I'm offering you protection.

53:58.803 --> 54:00.202
And if I say no?

54:00.304 --> 54:02.805
Then things would get
        rather unpleasant.

54:02.907 --> 54:04.940
The police
        would receive a call.

54:05.042 --> 54:08.077
Questions
                would be asked.

54:08.145 --> 54:10.412
Not an ideal situation
        for you

54:10.514 --> 54:11.981
or the children.

54:12.083 --> 54:13.449
No.

54:13.517 --> 54:16.518
What I'm proposing
            would work out
            for both of us.

54:18.756 --> 54:21.590
It'll be our little secret.

54:25.696 --> 54:26.629
How much?

54:27.698 --> 54:30.099
I'll take all the cash
        you have for now,

54:30.167 --> 54:31.900
and then we can
            figure out the rest.

54:31.969 --> 54:35.137
I think 25 grand
        would be about right.

54:35.206 --> 54:37.773
Where am I supposed to get
that kind of money?

54:37.875 --> 54:39.742
Where did you get
        all the money for this?

54:39.844 --> 54:41.844
Oh, I know.

54:41.946 --> 54:44.446
Your late wife's
             life insurance.

54:44.515 --> 54:46.382
What was it?
            Half a million?

54:46.450 --> 54:50.386
Funny how that
        all worked out for you.

55:13.811 --> 55:15.978
No one threatens my family.

55:23.721 --> 55:24.953
Matt Monroe?

55:25.823 --> 55:26.889
Yeah.

55:26.957 --> 55:28.657
You've been served.

55:28.726 --> 55:30.159
Have a nice day.

55:34.198 --> 55:37.599
Oh, God.

55:39.570 --> 55:42.805
-What do you want, Matt?
-A restraining order. Really?

55:42.907 --> 55:46.075
-You did this to yourself.
   -No, I didn't.

55:46.177 --> 55:49.011
Look, I think he has
something planned.

55:49.080 --> 55:50.479
<i>It has to do with you.</i>

55:50.548 --> 55:52.281
Do you hear yourself
      right now?

55:52.350 --> 55:54.116
You sound so paranoid.

55:54.185 --> 55:55.718
Okay, if I'm being
            so paranoid,

55:55.820 --> 55:58.420
why is the restraining order
    so wide I can't even
    go to our house?

55:58.489 --> 56:02.257
<i> Jenn, I can't even come home</i>
<i>with him living on our block.</i>

56:02.360 --> 56:04.727
I'm sure
        that's just standard.

56:04.829 --> 56:07.529
<i>It's-- It's not.</i>
<i>Trust me. I checked.</i>

56:07.598 --> 56:11.767
Look, I get things are
   not going well between us.

56:11.869 --> 56:14.903
I promised you
            I'm working on that.

56:14.972 --> 56:18.674
But why did you have
    to tell him about the clinic
    and the baby?

56:18.776 --> 56:20.642
I never said anything
    about that.

56:20.711 --> 56:23.979
You had to have
            because he threw it
            right into my face.

56:24.048 --> 56:25.714
I swear. I didn't tell him.

56:25.783 --> 56:27.716
Well, then how
                would he know?

56:28.953 --> 56:30.486
I don't know.

56:30.588 --> 56:32.755
<i>And you don't think</i>
<i>that is weird?</i>

56:32.823 --> 56:34.890
<i>Come on. Think of everything</i>
<i>that has happened.</i>

56:34.959 --> 56:36.558
I'll give him
        the night he found you.

56:36.627 --> 56:38.660
<i>But then moving in</i>
<i>across the street,</i>

56:38.729 --> 56:41.096
<i>and then me getting questioned</i>
<i>and arrested for assault?</i>

56:41.198 --> 56:43.132
<i>You think this is</i>
<i>all just coincidence?</i>

56:44.135 --> 56:45.868
I could have sworn
I locked the door,

56:45.936 --> 56:49.138
but somehow it was open
for the paramedics.

56:49.206 --> 56:53.475
Once I'm settled,
I can come by and help finish
setting up the baby's room.

56:53.544 --> 56:55.577
How did you know
    the nursery wasn't finished?

56:56.914 --> 56:58.380
I guessed.

57:02.720 --> 57:04.686
Listen, Matt, I hear you.
    I do.

57:04.755 --> 57:08.023
But I can't do this right now.
 Um, I'll have to call you back.

57:14.632 --> 57:15.664
Hey, Jenn.

57:15.766 --> 57:16.832
<i> Hey.</i>

57:16.901 --> 57:18.367
Um, I'm sorry to bother you.

57:18.436 --> 57:21.904
I was just wondering
if I could, um, ask you
for a huge favor.

57:22.006 --> 57:23.572
Absolutely.

57:23.674 --> 57:26.375
Um, I've run out
of a few things here,

57:26.444 --> 57:29.144
and I was wondering
if you would mind
running to the store for me.

57:29.246 --> 57:31.280
I'd be happy to watch the girls.

57:31.348 --> 57:33.649
Sure. Just give me the list
   and I'll drop the kids off.

57:33.751 --> 57:36.218
Great. Thanks. See you soon.

57:46.063 --> 57:47.362
-Hey.
            -Hey.

57:48.566 --> 57:50.766
Well, the girls
            are ready to rock.

57:50.835 --> 57:54.002
Definitely excited
   to spend some time
   with their Auntie Jennifer.

57:54.104 --> 57:56.505
Aw. Oh. Here's the list.

57:56.607 --> 57:57.973
Oh.

57:58.075 --> 57:59.508
That's it?

57:59.577 --> 58:02.211
Yeah. That's--
That's everything.
I don't know how I ran out.

58:02.279 --> 58:04.980
Oh, well, you've got
        more important things
        to focus on.

58:05.082 --> 58:06.849
Only a couple of days.

58:08.853 --> 58:11.386
Hey. You okay?
                 What's wrong?

58:11.455 --> 58:15.190
Oh, I'm okay.
I'm just a little stressed
about the delivery, that's all.

58:15.259 --> 58:18.160
All right.
        Well, I'll be back ASAP.

58:18.262 --> 58:19.561
I love you.

58:19.663 --> 58:20.562
Thanks again.

58:20.631 --> 58:21.797
Of course.

58:44.255 --> 58:45.120
Hey, Dad.

58:45.222 --> 58:46.455
Yeah, hon.

58:46.524 --> 58:47.756
I'm gonna go over
            to Garrett's

58:47.858 --> 58:49.892
because he forgot something
   for the girls.

58:49.960 --> 58:51.527
Can you just keep
